Games-ABC_Path-Generator

This is a generator for ABC Path puzzle games. It uses a portable random number
generator and different results can be specified using a different seed.

For more information, see:

* http://www.brainbashers.com/abcpath.asp

* http://www.shlomifish.org/open-source/projects/japanese-puzzle-games/abc-path/

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

	perl Build.PL
	./Build
	./Build test
	./Build install

SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION

After installing, you can find documentation for this module with the
perldoc command.

    perldoc Games::ABC_Path::Generator

You can also look for information at:

    RT, CPAN's request tracker (report bugs here)
        http://rt.cpan.org/NoAuth/Bugs.html?Dist=Games-ABC_Path-Generator

    AnnoCPAN, Annotated CPAN documentation
        http://annocpan.org/dist/Games-ABC_Path-Generator

    CPAN Ratings
        http://cpanratings.perl.org/d/Games-ABC_Path-Generator

    Search CPAN
        http://search.cpan.org/dist/Games-ABC_Path-Generator/


